CHANGED: Reworked the UHCI Root HUB Code.@{par}
BUGFIX: Fixed a short paket problem. (Reported by Jens Bagh)

 @{MC "V0.95"}

CHANGED: Reworked the whole transfer caching and setup mechanism. Now the stuff
