BUGFIX: Fixed the DMA problem on AmigaPCI systems.@{par}
FEATURE: The openpci version now autodetects the system and optimises DMA access
on Amithlon and Pegasos.@{par}
FEATURE: Removed the buffer specific user setup. The driver is using the best
method automaticaly.@{par}
BUGFIX: Fixed bug within the OHCI data toggle handling.@{par}
CHANGED: Several optimisations all over the global usb code.@{par}
FEATURE: USB2.0 (EHCI) root HUB and control and bulk transfer implemented. It's
not 100% done yet, but mass storage devices should already work with full speed.
