@node "Buglist" "Buglist"

@{MS "Buglist"}

Some devices aren't detected, if they are still connected at Poseidons startup. This
problem is known and happens on Amigasystems with an AmigaUSB-Controller, too!
Even Chris was unabled to say why this is happening. He told me that he spent
much time in finding the problem. Also without any luck.@{par}

This problem can be avoided by unplugging and reconnecting the device after
poseidon is running.@{par}

Currently there is no ISO Transfer. The only device with an AmigaOS driver which
uses ISO transfer are cameras. Unfortunatly my two cameras aren't supported.@{par}

Currently there is no way to work around this.@{par}

The EHCI support is not yet fully implemented. Several small feature need to be
implemented.@{par}

@endnode
